name: SOAKMONT V2
description: SOAK is a cryptocurrency powering the ecosystem of the future that will tokenize private equity assets.Our goal is to work with regulators to provide investors with a safe and proven framework for financing real estate projects on the blockchain.Subtokens will be created for each new asset and will represent the proof of ownership of the shares of a project. Each project can then use the SOAK ecosystem to distribute returns to asset owners all around the world.
